              <img alt="nDuo logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-nduo-100x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="Deeploi logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-deeploi-117x32@2x.png ">
              <img alt="Treeline logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-treeline-157x32@2x.png">
            </div>
            <div purpose="logo-row" class="d-flex flex-row align-items-center" :class="[isIosThirteen ? 'ios-13-scroll-animation' : isSafariThirteen ? 'safari-13-scroll-animation' : '']">
              <img alt="Amaris logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-amaris-86x32.png">
              <img alt="Denali logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-denali-55x32@2x.png ">
              <img alt="SHI logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-shi-70x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="Myriad logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-myriad-360-146x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="3eye logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-3eye-74x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="CDW logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-cdw-60x32@2x.png">
              <a href="https://eu1.hubs.ly/H0v39T-0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" no-icon><img alt="Primo logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-primo-108x32@2x.png"></a>
              <img alt="Wediggit logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-wediggit-94x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="Deel logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-deel-88x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="nDuo logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-nduo-100x32@2x.png">
              <img alt="Deeploi logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-deeploi-117x32@2x.png ">
              <img alt="Treeline logo" src="/images/logos/partner-logo-treeline-157x32@2x.png">
            </div>
            <div purpose="fade-left"></div>
            <div purpose="fade-right"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><%// page-hero %>

      <div purpose="section">
        <div purpose="section-heading">
          <h2>Two ways to partner</h2>
          <p>Fleet works with resellers who bring our platform to new customers and technology partners who build integrations that extend Fleet's capabilities.</p>
        </div>

        <div purpose="details-cards">
          <div purpose="details-card">
            <div>
              <p purpose="card-heading">Reseller partners</p>
              <p purpose="card-subheading">VARs, MSPs, and IT service providers</p>
            </div>
            <p>Sell Fleet to your customers with dedicated support from our team. You handle the relationship; we provide the platform, training, and technical enablement to help you close deals and deliver successful deployments.</p>
            <div purpose="checklist">
              <p>Deal registration and pipeline protection</p>
              <p>Sales engineering and pre-sales support</p>
              <p>Technical training and certification</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a purpose="cta-button" @click="clickOpenPartnerModal('reseller')">Apply to resell Fleet</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="details-card">
            <div>
              <p purpose="card-heading">Technology partners</p>
              <p purpose="card-subheading">ISVs, security vendors, and platform providers</p>
            </div>
            <p>Build integrations that connect your product with Fleet. Fleet's open API, webhook events, and osquery foundation make it straightforward to deliver joint value to shared customers.</p>
            <div purpose="checklist">
              <p>REST API and webhook integration support</p>
              <p>Access to Fleet's engineering team</p>
              <p>Early access to new APIs and features</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a purpose="cta-button" @click="clickOpenPartnerModal('integrations')">Become a technology partner</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div purpose="section">
        <div purpose="section-heading">
          <h2>Why choose Fleet</h2>
        </div>
        <div purpose="features-section">
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>Growing market opportunity</h5>
            <p>Organizations are moving away from legacy MDM vendors. Fleet's <a href="/handbook/company/why-this-way#why-open-source">open approach</a> is attracting enterprises like Stripe, Fastly, and Gusto.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>Multi-platform by default</h5>
            <p>macOS, Windows, Linux, iOS, Android, ChromeOS, and cloud infrastructure — all from one platform. One deal covers the entire fleet.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>Cloud or self-hosted</h5>
            <p>Let Fleet host it, or deploy on-prem, in any cloud, or air-gapped. 100% feature parity either way. Flexibility that opens doors other MDM vendors can't.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>GitOps-native</h5>
            <p>The only device management platform built for infrastructure-as-code. Peer-reviewed config changes, instant rollback, full audit trail.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>API-first architecture</h5>
            <p>Every feature accessible via REST API. Technology partners can build deep integrations without workarounds.</p>
          </div>
          <div purpose="feature">
            <h5>Open-source foundation</h5>
            <p>Fleet is built on open-source principles. Your customers can audit the code, verify what data is collected, and avoid vendor lock-in.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
  </div>
  <div purpose="banner-container">
    <div purpose="bottom-cta">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to partner with Fleet?</h2>
        <p>Talk to our team about how Fleet can help you deliver more value to your customers.</p>
      </div>
      <div purpose="button-row">
        <a purpose="cta-button" @click="clickOpenModal('partner')">
          Become a partner
        </a>
        <a @click="clickOpenModal('deal-registration')"><animated-arrow-button>Register a deal</animated-arrow-button></a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
  <%/* Cloud city banner */%>
  <parallax-city></parallax-city>
  <modal v-if="modal === 'partner'" @close="closeModal()">
    <div purpose="modal-form" v-if="!cloudSuccess">
      <div purpose="form-heading">
        <h2>Become a partner</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your business and how you’d like to partner with Fleet.</p>
      </div>
      <ajax-form :handle-submitting="handleSubmittingPartnerForm" :syncing.sync="syncing" :cloud-error.sync="cloudError" :form-errors.sync="formErrors" :form-data="partnerFormData" :form-rules="partnerFormRules" @submitted="submittedPartnerForm()">
        <div purpose="form-section" class="mt-0">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 pr-sm-2">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="partner-first-name">First name *</label>
                <input class="form-control" id="partner-first-name" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.submittersFirstName ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.submittersFirstName" autocomplete="first-name" >
                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersFirstName">Please enter your first name.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 pl-sm-2">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="parner-last-name">Last name *</label>
                <input class="form-control" id="parner-last-name" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.submittersLastName ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.submittersLastName" autocomplete="last-name" >
                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersLastName">Please enter your last name.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="partner-email-address">Email *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="partner-email-address"  :class="[formErrors.submittersEmailAddress ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.submittersEmailAddress" >
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersEmailAddress" focus-first>This doesn’t appear to be a valid email address</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="partner-organization">Company *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="partner-organization" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.submittersOrganization ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.submittersOrganization" >
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersOrganization">Please enter the name of your organization.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label purpose="checkbox-group-label">How will you work with Fleet? *</label>
            <label purpose="form-option" class="form-control" :class="[partnerFormData.partnerType === 'reseller' ? 'selected' : '']">
              <input type="radio" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.partnerType" value="reseller" >
              <span purpose="custom-radio"><span purpose="custom-radio-selected"></span></span>
              Resell or manage devices for customers
            </label>
            <label purpose="form-option" class="form-control" :class="[partnerFormData.partnerType === 'integrations' ? 'selected' : '']">
              <input type="radio" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.partnerType" value="integrations">
              <span purpose="custom-radio"><span purpose="custom-radio-selected"></span></span>
              Build integrations with Fleet
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="partner-website">Website *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="partner-website" :class="[formErrors.partnerWebsite ? 'is-invalid' : '']"  v-model.trim="partnerFormData.partnerWebsite" >
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.partnerWebsite">Please provide your website.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="partner-country">Country *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="partner-country" :class="[formErrors.partnerCountry ? 'is-invalid' : '']"  v-model.trim="partnerFormData.partnerCountry" >
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.partnerCountry">Please provide your country.</div>
          </div>
          <div v-if="partnerFormData.partnerType === 'reseller'">
            <label purpose="checkbox-group-label" for="partner-services-offered">Services offered *</label>
            <div class="form-group" :class="[formErrors.servicesOffered ? 'is-invalid' : '']">
              <div purpose="input-group">
                <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="device-management" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                  <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[partnerFormData.servicesOffered.mdm ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="partnerFormData['servicesOffered'].mdm" id="device-management">
                  MDM / endpoint management
                </label>
                <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="security-services" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                  <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[partnerFormData.servicesOffered.securityServices ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="partnerFormData['servicesOffered'].securityServices" id="security-services">
                  Security services (MSSP)
                </label>
                <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="it-services" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                  <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[partnerFormData.servicesOffered.itServices ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="partnerFormData['servicesOffered'].itServices" id="it-services">
                  IT services / MSP
                </label>
                <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="consulting" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                  <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[partnerFormData.servicesOffered.consulting ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                  <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="partnerFormData['servicesOffered'].consulting" id="consulting">
                  Consulting
                </label>
                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.servicesOffered">Please select an option.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="partner-number-of-hosts">Approx. endpoints managed *</label>
              <select class="form-control custom-select" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.numberOfHosts" :class="[formErrors.numberOfHosts ? 'is-invalid' : '']">
                <option :value="undefined">Select</option>
                <option value="1 - 100">1 - 100</option>
                <option value="100 - 1000">100 - 1,000</option>
                <option value="1000 - 5000">1,000 - 5,000</option>
                <option value="5000+">5,000+</option>
              </select>
              <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select an option.</div>
            </div>

          </div>
          <div v-else>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="partner-service-description">Which best describes your services? *</label>
              <select class="form-control custom-select" id="partner-service-description" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.servicesCategory" :class="[formErrors.servicesCategory ? 'is-invalid' : '']">
                <option :value="undefined">Select</option>
                <option value="Security">Security</option>
                <option value="Identity">Identity</option>
                <option value="Infrastructure / cloud">Infrastructure / cloud</option>
                <option value="Developer tools">Developer tools</option>
                <option value="IT operations">IT operations</option>
                <option value="Other">Other</option>
              </select>
              <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select an option.</div>
            </div>

          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <div purpose="form-label" v-if="partnerFormData.partnerType === 'reseller'">
              <label for="notes">Tell us about your services or customers *</label>
              <p>E.g., types of customers, deployments, or services you offer.</p>
            </div>
            <div purpose="form-label"  v-else>
              <label for="notes">Tell us about your integration *</label>
              <p>E.g., data integration, product integration, or co-marketing.</p>
            </div>
            <textarea class="form-control" :class="[formErrors.notes ? 'is-invalid' : '']" id="notes" type="textarea" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.notes" >
            </textarea>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please provide more information</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div purpose="hp-input" aria-hidden="true">
          <label>Website</label>
          <input name="website-url" type="text" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" v-model.trim="partnerFormData.websiteUrl">
        </div>
        <cloud-error purpose="cloud-error" v-if="cloudError === 'invalidEmailDomain'">
          <p>
            Please enter your work email address.
          </p>
        </cloud-error>
        <cloud-error purpose="cloud-error" v-else-if="cloudError"></cloud-error>
        <ajax-button purpose="submit-button" spinner="true" type="submit" :syncing="syncing" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary mt-4" v-if="!cloudError">Submit</ajax-button>
        <ajax-button purpose="submit-button" type="button" :syncing="syncing" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary mt-4" v-if="cloudError" @click="clickResetForm()">Try again</ajax-button>
      </ajax-form>
    </div>
    <div v-else>
      <h2>Thanks for registering</h2>
      <p>A member of our team will be in touch soon.</p>
    </div>
  </modal>


  <modal v-if="modal === 'deal-registration'" @close="closeModal()">
    <div purpose="modal-form" v-if="!cloudSuccess">
      <div purpose="form-heading">
        <h2>Register a deal</h2>
        <p>Not a partner yet? Submit anyway and we’ll follow up.</p>
      </div>
      <ajax-form action="deliverDealRegistrationSubmission" :syncing.sync="syncing" :cloud-error.sync="cloudError" :form-errors.sync="formErrors" :form-data="dealRegistrationFormData" :form-rules="dealRegistrationFormRules" @submitted="submittedDealForm()">
        <div purpose="form-section" class="mt-0">
          <h3>Partner details</h3>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 pr-sm-2">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="submitter-first-name">First name *</label>
                <input class="form-control" id="submitter-first-name" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.partnersFirstName ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submittersFirstName" autocomplete="first-name">
                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersFirstName">Please enter your first name.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 pl-sm-2">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="submitter-last-name">Last name *</label>
                <input class="form-control" id="submitter-last-name" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.submittersLastName ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submittersLastName" autocomplete="last-name">
                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersLastName">Please enter your last name.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="submitters-email-address">Email *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="submitters-email-address"  :class="[formErrors.submittersEmailAddress ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submittersEmailAddress">
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersEmailAddress" focus-first>This doesn’t appear to be a valid email address</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="submitters-organization">Company *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="submitters-organization" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.submittersOrganization ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submittersOrganization">
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submittersOrganization">Please enter the name of your organization.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group" :class="[formErrors.submitterIsExistingPartner ? 'is-invalid' : '']" >
            <strong>Are you an existing Fleet partner *</strong>
            <label purpose="form-option" class="form-control" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.submitterIsExistingPartner === 'yes' ? 'selected' : '']">
              <input type="radio" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submitterIsExistingPartner" value="yes" >
              <span purpose="custom-radio"><span purpose="custom-radio-selected"></span></span>
              Yes
            </label>
            <label purpose="form-option" class="form-control" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.submitterIsExistingPartner === 'no' ? 'selected' : '']">
              <input type="radio" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.submitterIsExistingPartner" value="no">
              <span purpose="custom-radio"><span purpose="custom-radio-selected"></span></span>
              No
            </label>
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.submitterIsExistingPartner" focus-first>Please select an option</div>
            <div purpose="new-partner-note" v-if="dealRegistrationFormData.submitterIsExistingPartner === 'no'">
              Not a partner yet? No problem, we’ll follow up to get you set up.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div purpose="form-section">
          <h3>Customer details</h3>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="customer-organization">Company *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="customer-organization"  :class="[formErrors.customersOrganization ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.customersOrganization">
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.customersOrganization" focus-first>Please enter the customer's company</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="customer-name">Contact name *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="customer-name" type="text"  :class="[formErrors.customersName ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.customersName" autocomplete="first-name">
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.customersName">Please enter the customer's name.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="customers-email-address">Contact email *</label>
            <input class="form-control" id="customers-email-address"  :class="[formErrors.customersEmailAddress ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.customersEmailAddress">
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.customersEmailAddress" focus-first>This doesn’t appear to be a valid email address</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div purpose="form-section">
          <h3>Deal qualification</h3>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="deal-stage">Deal stage *</label>
            <select class="form-control custom-select" id="deal-stage"  :class="[formErrors.dealStage ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.dealStage">
              <option :value="undefined">Select</option>
              <option value="Identified">Identified</option>
              <option value="In discussion">In discussion</option>
              <option value="Evaluating">Evaluating</option>
              <option value="Late stage">Late stage</option>
            </select>
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.dealStage" focus-first>Please select a deal stage</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="expected-close">Expected close *</label>
            <select class="form-control custom-select" id="expected-close" :class="[formErrors.expectedClose ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.expectedClose">
              <option :value="undefined">Select</option>
              <option value="< 1 month">< 1 month</option>
              <option value="1-3 months">1-3 months</option>
              <option value="3-6 months">3-6 months</option>
              <option value="6+ months">6+ months</option>
            </select>
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.expectedClose" focus-first>Please select an option</div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="reseller-number-of-devices">Estimated number of devices *</label>
            <select class="form-control custom-select" :class="[formErrors.numberOfHosts ? 'is-invalid' : '']" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.numberOfHosts">
              <option :value="undefined">Select</option>
              <option value="1 - 100">1 - 100</option>
              <option value="100 - 1000">100 - 1,000</option>
              <option value="1000 - 5000">1,000 - 5,000</option>
              <option value="5000+">5,000+</option>
            </select>
            <div class="invalid-feedback">Please select an option.</div>
          </div>


          <label purpose="checkbox-group-label" for="deal-reg-platforms">Platforms *</label>
          <div purpose="checkbox-group" class="form-group d-flex flex-column" :class="[formErrors.platforms ? 'is-invalid' : '']">
              <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="apple" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.platforms.apple ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['platforms'].apple" id="apple">
                Apple (macOS, iOS/iPadOS)
              </label>
              <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="windows" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.platforms.windows ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['platforms'].windows" id="windows">
                Windows
              </label>
              <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="linux" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.platforms.linux ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['platforms'].linux" id="linux">
                Linux
              </label>
              <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="other" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
                <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.platforms.other ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
                <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['platforms'].other" id="other">
                Others (Android, ChromeOS)
              </label>
              <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.platforms" focus-first>Please select an option</div>
          </div>

          <label purpose="checkbox-group-label" for="deal-reg-use-case">Use case *</label>
        <div purpose="checkbox-group" class="form-group d-flex flex-column" :class="[formErrors.useCase ? 'is-invalid' : '']">
            <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="mdm" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
              <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.useCase.mdm ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
              <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['useCase'].mdm" id="mdm">
              Device management
            </label>
            <label purpose="custom-checkbox-label" for="security" @click="clickSelectCustomCheckbox()">
              <span purpose="custom-checkbox" :class="[dealRegistrationFormData.useCase.security ? 'checked' : '']" ><span purpose="custom-checkbox-check"></span></span>
              <input type="checkbox" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData['useCase'].security" id="security">
              Security / compliance
            </label>
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.useCase" focus-first>Please select an option</div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="deal-notes">Additional notes *</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="deal-notes" type="textarea" :class="[formErrors.notes ? 'is-invalid' : '']"  v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.notes"></textarea>
            <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="formErrors.notes" focus-first>Please provide more information</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div purpose="hp-input" aria-hidden="true">
          <label>Website</label>
          <input name="website-url" type="text" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" v-model.trim="dealRegistrationFormData.websiteUrl">
        </div>
        <cloud-error purpose="cloud-error" v-if="cloudError === 'invalidEmailDomain'">
          <p>
            Please enter your work email address.
          </p>
        </cloud-error>
        <cloud-error purpose="cloud-error" v-else-if="cloudError"></cloud-error>
        <p class="small">By submitting you agree to our <a href="/legal/privacy">privacy policy</a> and <a href="/terms">terms of service</a>.</p>
        <ajax-button purpose="submit-button" spinner="true" type="submit" :syncing="syncing" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary mt-4" v-if="!cloudError">Submit</ajax-button>
        <ajax-button purpose="submit-button" type="button" :syncing="syncing" class="btn btn-block btn-lg btn-primary mt-4" v-if="cloudError" @click="clickResetForm()">Try again</ajax-button>
      </ajax-form>
    </div>
    <div v-else>
      <h2>Thanks for registering</h2>
      <p>A member of our team will be in touch soon.</p>
    </div>
  </modal>
</div>
<%- /* Expose server-rendered data as window.SAILS_LOCALS :: */ exposeLocalsToBrowser() %>
